name: Feelings and Mind
description: Wild energy still lives in us and instincts guide our activities. No matter how civilized we become. It is important for a person to feel the integrity of him/herself, to be in contact both with mind and with feelings and instincts. The more we are cut off from our wild essence, the more it seems to us that this is reasonable and it needs to be that way. But only by allowing ourselves to be manifested in different facets, we can feel harmony and happiness.  2048x2048 px ~olay.ana~
